               <msContents>
                  <summary>Mystagogia, ትምህርተ፡ ኅቡዓት፡, The different ôrawit mla’ǝktihu prayers of the different anaphoras, Time table for the use of the different anaphoras, Table blessing, Litanical prayer to Jesus Christ, "For the sake of your. . .", Halleluiatic hymn to the Trinity, Calendar of the feasts of the year, Greetings to Mary, Hymns to the Martyr George, "Come, George", Rogation of the Archangel Michael, Hymn to Mary, "In the name of the Father and the Son"</summary>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <locus from="1v" to="8v" facs="002">Fols 1v–8v</locus>
                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2444Temher">Tǝmhǝrta
                                                  ḫǝbuʾāt</title>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                    <locus from="9r" to="13v" facs="009">Fols 9r–13v</locus>
                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4942Sarawita">Śarāwita
                                                  malāʾǝktihu la-Madḫāne ʿĀlam</title>
                    <notatedMusic>
                    <desc>with musical notations
                    </desc></notatedMusic>
                    <note>From a selection of anaophoras</note>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                    <locus from="13v" to="14v" facs="014">Fols 13v–14v</locus>
                    <title>Timetable for the use of the different anaphoras</title>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                    <locus from="14v" to="16r" facs="015">Fols 14v–16r</locus>
                    <title type="complete" cert="medium" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6205Saalnaka">Saʾalnāka maḥari
                                                  saʾalnāka faṭāri saʾalnāka kahali</title>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                    <locus from="17v" to="19r" facs="018">Fols 17v–19r</locus>
                    <title>Litanical prayer to Jesus Christ, <q>“For the sake of your …,”</q></title>
                    <note>Incomplete and beginning</note>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      በእን[ተ፡] አስተርዮትከ፡ በእን፡ ጾምከ፡ በእን፡ ሕማምከ፡ በእን፡ ተዕህዞትከ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>
                    </incipit>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i6">
                    <locus from="19r" to="21r" facs="019">Fols 19r–21r</locus>
                    <title>Halleluiatic hymn to the Trinity</title>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ለአብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ መላእክቲሆሙ፡ ለሥሉስ፡ እሩፀቶሙ፡ ለነፋስ፡ ሃሌ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>
                    </incipit>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i7">
                    <locus from="21v" to="22r" facs="022">Fols 21v–22r</locus>
                    <title>Calendar of the feasts of the year</title>
                    <note>Incomplete at the end, erased to make room for the forged painting</note>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i8">
                     <locus from="23v" to="26r" facs="024">Fols 23v–26r</locus>
                    <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2962RepCh243">Hymn to Our Lady
                                                  Mary</title>
                    <note>Incomplete at the beginning</note>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i9">
                    <locus from="26r" to="32r" facs="026">Fols 26r–32r</locus>
                    <title>Hymn to the Martyr George, "Come, George," <foreign xml:lang="gez">ነዓ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡</foreign>
                     </title>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      ነዓ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ እንዘ፡ ትጼአን፡ በፈረስ። ወነዓ፡ ፍቁርየ፡ ዘልዳ፡ ንጉሥ።
                    </incipit>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i10">
                    <locus from="32r" to="36v" facs="032">Fols 32r–36v</locus>
                    <title>Rogation of the Archangel Michael, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ምህላ፡ ዘሚካኤል፡</foreign>
                     </title>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      መልአኩ፡ ለቃል፡ ሚካኤል፡ መልአኩ።ለቃል፡ መልአኩ፡ ለቃል፡ ፻፡ ሚካኤል፡ መጋቤ፡ ኵሉ፡ ለበፍሰ፡ ኵሉ፡ ፍጥረት። አምሕለከ፡ በጸባዖት። ምህላነ፡ ስምዓ፡ በዛቲ፡ ዕለት።
                    </incipit>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i11">
                    <locus from="36v" to="45v" facs="037">Fols 36v–45v</locus>
                    <title>Hymn to Mary, "In the Name of the Father and the Son," <foreign xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡</foreign>
                     </title>
                    <note>Incomplete at the end, erased to make room for painting. Composed following the psalms of David</note>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ሥላሴ። ብሂልየ፡ ወጠንኩ፡ ዘከሊ፡ ውዳሴ።
                    </incipit>
                  </msItem>

               </msContents>
